data.name: label3.Text
data.value: Note 1. Your email will be recorded. Your email will be used as your identity. 2. We will extract your roll number from your email to record your mess attendance. Therefore, submit your response carefully and do not submit your attendance using someone other's email account. 3. You have to submit your response before 11.59 PM for the next day menu. If anyone submitted the form after the mentioned time for current date then his attendance will not be considered. 4. You can submit the google form for future dates. 5. However, once you submit a form then your response would not change. So plz submit the form carefully. If you did not select any meal option at first submission then you can submit another form to select the missing option before 11.59 PM. 6. However, your responses of first submission would not change even if you deselect in second submission. Alert: Students who did not pay their dues yet, will be considered as default and will not be served with meal. If you did not pay mess dues yet then do not submit the form as the RFID machine will not allow you while your attendance will be marked in the system.
